    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><br><strong>梦中影</strong>是一款2D心理恐怖冒险游戏。<br><br>迷失于清醒的梦中，在现实与虚幻之间游离。极尽利用你的奇异相机在神秘的鬼魂居所中探索，在清晰又如梦般的世界中找到你在此的意义。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127060/extras/c482e3690f6100ee43dcbd67511f94c3.poster.avif?t=1745229869\" width=630 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127060/extras/c482e3690f6100ee43dcbd67511f94c3.webm?t=1745229869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127060/extras/c482e3690f6100ee43dcbd67511f94c3.mp4?t=1745229869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br>探索只有鬼魂居住的未知地域，在推进扣人心弦的故事的过程中收集物品、解开谜题。透过奇异相机的镜头，拍摄高亮物体并与之交互。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127060/extras/42af8594069f6a2a017fcda81416065f.poster.avif?t=1745229869\" width=630 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127060/extras/42af8594069f6a2a017fcda81416065f.webm?t=1745229869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127060/extras/42af8594069f6a2a017fcda81416065f.mp4?t=1745229869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>独特的2D横版美术风格<br></li><li>透过奇异相机的镜头与隐藏物品交互<br></li><li>氛围十足的音乐与音效设计<br></li><li>深入探索清晰又如梦般的世界，在现实与虚幻之间游离<br></li><li>极简且实用的界面，让玩家沉浸于故事中不被打扰<br></li><li>芬兰独立制作人出品，所有游戏素材皆为原创！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127060/extras/c7f85c4d3a9bebc969ff47f05f92da5b.poster.avif?t=1745229869\" width=630 height=230 ><source src=\"https